50|$|The Dunedin mayoral election, 2013 {{was held}} on Saturday, 12 October 2013 and was {{conducted}} under the <b>single</b> <b>transferable</b> <b>voting</b> system. Dave Cull, Dunedin's 57th mayor, was re-elected after seeing off eight challengers.|$|R
